---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for the Gregory the Great Institute website.">

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose-section">
      <h1 data-pagefind-weight="10">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <div class="prose">
        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          The Gregory the Great Institute collects the following types of information from users of our
          website and services: names, contact details (email, phone, address), event registration
          information, donation and payment details, website usage data through cookies and analytics,
          volunteer and staff records, and newsletter subscription preferences.
        </p>

        <h2>How We Collect Information</h2>
        <p>
          We collect information through: online forms (contact, registration, newsletter signup),
          donation and subscription forms, email and phone correspondence, cookies and website analytics
          (Cloudflare Web Analytics), and in-person event signups.
        </p>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>
          Your information is used for: sending newsletters and communications (via ActiveCampaign),
          processing donations and issuing tax receipts, administering programs and events, managing
          volunteers and staff, and improving our website and services.
        </p>

        <h2>Data Storage & Security</h2>
        <p>
          We store data in password-protected systems with encryption where applicable. Physical records
          are kept in locked files. Access is limited to authorized staff and contractors on a need-to-know
          basis. We conduct periodic security reviews and train staff on data handling procedures.
        </p>

        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          We use the following services which may process your data: Sanity (content management), Cloudflare
          (hosting and analytics), ActiveCampaign (email marketing), Stripe (payment processing), and Zeffy
          (donation processing via Catholic Voices Canada). We do not sell or rent your personal information.
        </p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          You have the right to: access the personal information we hold about you, request corrections to
          inaccurate information, withdraw consent for communications at any time, and request deletion of
          your data where applicable.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For questions about this privacy policy or to exercise your rights, contact us at
          <a href="mailto:info@gregorythegreat.ca">info@gregorythegreat.ca</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose-section {
    max-width: var(--max-prose-width);
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .prose-section h1 {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .last-updated {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .prose h2 {
    margin-top: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
</style>
